    "The prompting strategy is designed whereby provided a source sequence S = [s 1, s 2,..., s |S| ] and a target sequence T = [t 1, t 2,..., t |T | ] the prompt will interleave subsequences from S and T leveraging delimiting tokens to separate the subsequences.",
